Install python,pip.

Register for the Journey Planner timetables at http://www.tfl.gov.uk/businessandpartners/syndication/16492.aspx

Put your email in the feed URL in update.sh

Requires libxml2-dev libxslt-dev, installation on debian/ubuntu:

apt-get install libxml2-dev libxslt-dev

Then:

pip install -r requirements.txt

To run do (it will take a while):

./update.sh
python last_tube_from_loc.py

Add update.sh to your crontab, the data refreshes once a week I think.
